<big><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-weight: bold;">COGRIM -
Clustering of Genes into Regulons using Integrated Modeling</span></big><br>
<hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;"><br>
This tool is an R program implementation of the gibbs sampler for
COGRIM. To learn about R, please visit <a
 href="http://www.r-project.org/">The R Project for Statistical
Computing</a>.<br>
<br>
The R source code is available free under the general <a
 href="CBIL_License.html">CBIL software agreement</a>.<br>
Please email questions to <a href="mailto:ggchen@pcbi.upenn.edu">ggchen@pcbi.upenn.edu</a><br>
<br>
